directions.dialogText: Use the functions \`move()\`, \`rotate()\` and \`getPart()\` to direct the Space Ranger pick up the sphere.

levels.mission: Get the Space Ranger to each sphere. On each square with a sphere, call the function getPart() to pick up the sphere.
levels.tools:
\`move()\` move forward one square

\`rotate()\` rotate 90 degrees

\`getPart()\` pick up a sphere
